íŸ@8bc2ac15ed7828fee57b4e4b2c0a6d4413dcaa8af2274e66c9c8c2a512f82b86⁄>Title: title: polars selector all
Path: Examples
Content:
Create a selector for all columns
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> polars selector all


```
Multiply all columns by 2 using with-column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]]
                    | polars into-df
                    | polars with-column ((polars selector all) * 2)
                    | polars collect
